snippet.title: SteamWorld Build - Official Gameplay Trailer | The MIX Showcase March 2023
snippet.description: Explore the mine, take on enemies, and check out gameplay in this latest trailer for SteamWorld Build, an upcoming game coming to PC and consoles in 2023.
